  "description": "Thinking about the influence that Terry Pratchett has had on my writing, specifically my writing style, and how every sentence can probably be written to be a little fun.\nAnd it made me think about how, in linguistics, there\u0026rsquo;s the idea of pragmatics, the parts of speech that make it sound human, or whatever. And it makes me wonder about the idea of \u0026ldquo;ludimatics\u0026rdquo; or whatever the proper formation would be: the parts of speech that make it feel fun.\n",
  "name": "2025-09-02, 2005h, Linguistic pragmatics and ludimatics",
